					<h3 style="color:gray">Sending a Sample for Research</h3>
					In sending a sample, you are required to first fill up a form. This form asks for general information, pest problem, and additional information. After filling up, package the sample and indicate the control number of the form before sending to the laboratory.
					<br/><br/>
					Note that you need to be logged in into your account to submit the form.
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="mdl-grid">
